thanks for this wonderful song .I dont know my comment will justify this song or not but since I listened this song, I am repeating it almost 25 or 35 times. I havent listen such melody before, which always my first priority when I listen a song. Xulfi bhai you did a extra ordinary job with the music, compostion and lyrics. Unforgettable song. Pakistani music at its best and now its showing that music roots in Pakistan where we produced so much talented artist like Nusrat sb and Mehdi Hassan Sb. Although music listen so much our neigbhour country but its roots here in Pakistan. Xulfi bhai you have done so much hard work in this song and block buster which paid off now. Thanks for giving us such songs in 2024.❤
@cokestudio love from India
